&lt;h3 id="fonts-and-colours"&gt;Fonts and Colours
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pick some colours, not too many and stick with them. Pick some fonts, not too many and stick with them. I chose pastels for a dreamy, hazy vibe. There needs to be a pink and a teal, in my case Mulberry and RobinEggBlue.&lt;/p&gt;
